Don-Mendo version 0.0.5

This is a Perl-lization of an Spanish play called "La Venganza de Don
Mendo". Main intention was to use it to teach POE, but who knows what
other fate might await it.

Check out the examples also at
http://github.com/JJ/la-venganza-de-don-mendo/tree/master/poe-examples 

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

None.


